---
title: Harissa Spiced Haddock Fishcakes with veg and aioli drizzle
description: If you're a fan of fish then you're going to adore these harissa spiced fishcakes. Made with haddock and creamy mashed potato, these fishcakes are fried to crispy perfection, bursting with flavour, and accompanied by tender roasted veg.
